- It's OK, it's OK. They're dead. They're dead.

745
01:13:58,295 --> 01:13:59,694
Come on.

746
01:14:10,335 --> 01:14:12,291
My car's parked up on the main road.

747
01:14:12,335 --> 01:14:14,769
There's, there's keys in the truck.

748
01:14:16,135 --> 01:14:18,171
