Hold on, I'll be right back.

751
01:14:48,135 --> 01:14:50,046
Where are you going?

752
01:14:50,095 --> 01:14:52,165
- The kid's inside. I gotta go get him.
- No!

753
01:14:52,215 --> 01:14:55,810
Aargh! Don't worry, I'll be back.
It'll just take a second.

754
01:14:55,855 --> 01:14:57,732
No, he's the devil!

755
01:14:58,775 --> 01:15:00,652
Angie, it's gonna be OK.

756
01:15:00,695 --> 01:15:02,094
No, it's not!

757
01:15:02,135 --> 01:15:05,127
No, we have to go! We have to go!

758
01:15:05,175 --> 01:15:06,767
- (Slashing)
- (Screams)

759
01:15:08,815 --> 01:15:10,453
(Sobs)

760
01:15:10,495 --> 01:15:11,974
No, please!

761
01:15:12,015 --> 01:15:14,734
- (Whimpers)
- (Groans)

762
01:15:14,775 --> 01:15:16,128
(Sobs)

763
01:15:22,015 --> 01:15:24,131
Oh, please!

764
01:15:25,535 --> 01:15:26,934
Let me out of here!

765
01:15:28,015 --> 01:15:30,051
Hungry.

766
01:15:30,095 --> 01:15:31,733
Please, let me out of here!

767
01:15:33,215 --> 01:15:36,446
- (Screams)
- Hungry.

768
01:15:36,495 --> 01:15:40,534
(Sobs) Stay away from me.
Stay away from me, please!

769
01:15:41,655 --> 01:15:43,168
(Screams)

770
01:15:43,215 --> 01:15:45,604
- (Screams)
- Hungry.

771
01:15:45,655 --> 01:15:47,247
(Screams)

772
01:15:57,175 --> 01:15:58,813
(Rattles door)

773
01:15:58,855 --> 01:16:00,686
(Gasps) Go away!

774
01:16:07,215 --> 01:16:08,648
(Knife rattling on wood)

775
01:16:13,735 --> 01:16:15,487
(Electrical buzz)

776
01:16:19,695 --> 01:16:21,094
(Screams)

777
01:16:25,535 --> 01:16:27,014
(Gasping) Sam?

778
01:16:33,935 --> 01:16:35,368
Sam, look.

779
01:16:35,415 --> 01:16:37,975
There plenty of food in here for you.

780
01:16:38,015 --> 01:16:39,573
See?

781
01:16:39,615 --> 01:16:41,685
Sam, you don't have to eat me.

782
01:16:44,735 --> 01:16:46,327
Sam?

783
01:16:48,735 --> 01:16:50,134
- (Slashing sound)
- (Screams)

784
01:16:50,175 --> 01:16:52,166
(Gasps)

785
01:16:52,215 --> 01:16:54,729
- No, Sam, please.
- Hungry.

786
01:16:54,775 --> 01:16:56,766
(Gasps) Please, Sam. Stop.

787
01:16:56,815 --> 01:16:58,487
Hungry!

788
01:16:59,535 --> 01:17:01,207
(Cries)

789
01:17:11,655 --> 01:17:13,168
- (Grunts)
- (Growling)

790
01:17:13,215 --> 01:17:15,206
(Growls continuously)

791
01:17:36,775 --> 01:17:38,527
- Still hungry?
- (Growls)

792
01:17:38,575 --> 01:17:40,088
Well, choke on this.

793
01:17:40,135 --> 01:17:41,534
(Whack)

794
