800
01:19:25,095 --> 01:19:26,813
(Man 2) She's lost a lot of blood.

801
01:19:27,855 --> 01:19:29,527
- And she's in a coma.
- Uh-huh.

802
01:19:29,575 --> 01:19:33,966
You know, I, uh,
I don't know when she'll come out of it.

803
01:19:34,015 --> 01:19:35,414
OK.

804
01:19:35,455 --> 01:19:37,366
But when she does, you let me know.

805
01:19:39,815 --> 01:19:43,603
Goddamn slaughterhouse out there.
We need some answers.

806
01:19:43,655 --> 01:19:46,294
Doctor, look, she's awake.

807
01:19:50,815 --> 01:19:53,773
Angie... Can you blink for me?

808
01:19:55,295 --> 01:19:56,489
Good.

809
01:19:56,535 --> 01:19:58,765
Can you see better now?

810
01:20:00,295 --> 01:20:01,330
Angie?

811
01:20:01,375 --> 01:20:03,969
No! No! No!

812
01:20:04,015 --> 01:20:08,327
Angie, it's OK. It's OK, you're safe.
Nurse! Nurse!

813
01:20:08,375 --> 01:20:10,764
You're safe. You're safe.

814
01:20:10,815 --> 01:20:11,884
Rick?

815
01:20:11,935 --> 01:20:13,084
Yeah.

816
01:20:13,135 --> 01:20:16,571
Oh, God, Rick.
Oh, please don't leave me.

817
01:20:16,615 --> 01:20:18,890
No, I'm not going anywhere.

818
01:20:20,615 --> 01:20:24,130
Angie, I'm gonna
have to ask you a couple questions.

819
01:20:24,175 --> 01:20:25,847
Can't you give her a little time?

820
01:20:25,895 --> 01:20:27,647
No, son, I'm sorry, I can't.

821
01:20:27,695 --> 01:20:31,005
Now, Angie, your friend here said
you were babysitting. Is that correct?

822
01:20:31,055 --> 01:20:33,171
Yes.

823
01:20:33,215 --> 01:20:35,445
Can you remember
what happened to the child?

824
01:20:35,495 --> 01:20:37,053
What do you mean?

825
01:20:37,095 --> 01:20:38,574
We couldn't find him.

826
01:20:38,615 --> 01:20:39,650
What?

827
01:20:39,695 --> 01:20:41,970
We found Chief Dinneli,

828
01:20:42,015 --> 01:20:43,414
the parents,

829
01:20:43,455 --> 01:20:46,253
and 20 female bodies
buried in the backyard.

830
01:20:46,295 --> 01:20:47,933
None of them were children.

831
01:20:47,975 --> 01:20:51,251
But he was in the barn.
He was in the barn!

832
01:20:52,415 --> 01:20:54,292
Angie, try and remember exactly...

833
01:20:54,335 --> 01:20:56,291
- Let her be.
...where you last saw him.

834
01:20:56,335 --> 01:20:58,690
- Miss, can I help you?
- I'm her mother.

835
01:20:58,735 --> 01:21:02,171
- Mom!
- It's OK, baby. I'm here now.

836
01:21:05,575 --> 01:21:10,091
- I'll be outside if you need anything, OK, Angie?
- No, Rick, stay. Please, stay.

837
01:21:13,215 --> 01:21:15,126
We need to pray.

